<template>

      fullscreen

          </v-btn>
          <v-toolbar-title>Carrito</v-toolbar-title>
          <v-spacer></v-spacer>
        </v-toolbar>

        <v-container class="pt-12"> </v-container>
      </v-card>
    </v-dialog>
  </v-row>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "Carrito",
  data() {
    return {
      dialog: false,
    };
  },
  methods: {
    cancelar() {
      this.dialog = false;
    },
  },
};
</script>
